# Gallery & Media Rules

## Gallery Item Schema
Every item in `galleryItems` must match this shape:
```ts
type GalleryItem = {
  id: string                                    // unique, sequential: '1', '2', ...
  title: string                                 // judul pekerjaan dalam Bahasa Indonesia
  category: GalleryCategory                     // must match `categories` array
  type: 'before-after' | 'photo' | 'video'
  before?: string        // '/gallery/before/filename.jpg' (required if type=before-after)
  after?: string         // '/gallery/after/filename.jpg'  (required if type=before-after)
  photo?: string         // '/gallery/filename.jpg'         (required if type=photo)
  youtubeId?: string     // video ID only, NOT full URL     (for type=video YouTube)
  videoSrc?: string      // '/gallery/videos/filename.mp4'  (for type=video local)
  description?: string   // deskripsi singkat opsional
}
```

## Valid Categories
```ts
type GalleryCategory =
  | 'Turbocharger'
  | 'Mesin'
  | 'Pompa'
  | 'Governor'
  | 'Kelistrikan'
  | 'Lainnya'
```
If adding a new category, also add it to the `categories` array in `app/galeri/page.tsx`.

## File Naming Convention
```
/public/gallery/before/[service]-[number].jpg    e.g. turbo-01.jpg
/public/gallery/after/[service]-[number].jpg     e.g. turbo-01.jpg
/public/gallery/[service]-[number].jpg           e.g. pompa-01.jpg
/public/gallery/videos/[service]-[number].mp4    e.g. governor-01.mp4
```

## Image Requirements
- Format: JPG or WebP (prefer WebP for performance)
- Aspect ratio: 16:9 (landscape) for consistency in grid
- Max file size: 500KB per image (optimize before upload)
- Min resolution: 1200×675px

## Video Requirements
- YouTube: public or unlisted videos only
- Local .mp4: max 10MB, H.264 encoding, 720p recommended
- Always provide `title` attribute for accessibility

## BeforeAfterSlider Usage
```tsx
<BeforeAfterSlider
  before="/gallery/before/turbo-01.jpg"
  after="/gallery/after/turbo-01.jpg"
  beforeLabel="Sebelum"   // default
  afterLabel="Sesudah"    // default
  title="Judul opsional"
  alt="Deskripsi alt text"
/>
```

## Adding New Category (full steps)
1. Add string to `categories` array in `app/galeri/page.tsx`
2. Add `GalleryCategory` type union in the type definition
3. Add items with that category in `galleryItems`

## Lightbox
Photo items (`type: 'photo'`) support lightbox zoom on click.
Before/after and video items do NOT use lightbox (they have their own interaction).

## Performance
- Images are loaded with `next/image` (`fill` + `object-cover`)
- Lazy loading is automatic via Next.js
- Do NOT add `priority` prop to gallery images (they are below the fold)
